<h1>CP1406 - Assignment 2 - Project Plan</h1>
<h1>Diazepam Cafe (Ice-Cream Cafe)</h1>
<h3>Group member : Bilal , Dou wei , Wei siyuan</h3>

<h3>Mission Statement</h3>
<p>Attract more people to the an independent icecream and desserts café，enhance the influence cause people to invest.</p>
<h3>Success Evaluation </h3>
<p>whether people come to the café and buy the ice cream which is website recommend.</p>
<h3>Target Audience </h3>
<p>The target of this website is young people and children, so design this website more lovely and put the logo of ice cream in the Prominent location.Also </p>
<h3>Content</h3>
<ul>
  <li>The homepage displays a large picture of our products, which intends to grab viewer&rsquo;s interest and attention in what the café sells. From here, users can access the rest of the main pages by clicking the navigation bar.</li>
  <li>The products page will display all the products on offer, a brief description of the product in text, and a small image displaying the product. Clicking the product will link the users to the product page, will describe the product more in depth. The products page will also contain a link to an online order form for customers to make online purchases.</li>
  <li>The events page will show users of the upcoming events taking place in the café, in list form, sorted by date with the closest event placed first. Include information on children&rsquo;s fashion show as well.</li>
  <li>The services page will provide information on the café&rsquo;s delivery policies and the party offers that the café serves. From here, customers are linked to the online feedback form in order for them to help the café improve.</li>
  <li>The about us page will display information about the organization as a whole, and provide links to the café&rsquo;s social media pages. This will also show the relevant contact information of the café.</li>
</ul>
